import { FcDeleteDatabase } from "react-icons"


const CartItem = (item, itemIndex) => {
    return <div >

        <
        div >
        <
        div >
        <
        img src = { item.image }
    /> < /
    div >

        <
        div >
        <
        h1 > { item.title } < /h1>

    <
    h1 > { item.description } < /h1> < /
        div >

        <
        p > { item.price } < /p>

    <
    div > < FcDeleteDatabase / > < /div>




    <
    /div>


    <
    /div>;
};

export default CartItem;
